deploy-routeviews-py

A script to quickly deploy routeviews-py on a Linux machine. Simply specify which ASNs should be monitored. deploy-routeviews-py will:
-Download the latest copy of routeviews-py
-Update your crontab appropriately
-Create a PHP file which uses Highcharts to visualize the BGP data

This script can be used to quickly setup BGP monitoring on specific ASNs when internet censorship via BGP manipulation is suspected.

Usage: ./deploy-routeviews-py.sh 123,456,789 (comma-seperated ASNs)
Installation will occur in the current directory.
